# ========================================
# WHITELIST IMPORTANT FILES
# (These should NOT be ignored)
# ========================================

# Always include these important files
!README.md
!LICENSE
!CONTRIBUTING.md
!requirements.txt
!package.json
!.env.example
!.gitignore
!.github/
!deployment/
!docs/
!system_health_checks/README.md

# Include important config templates
!config.template.json
!settings.example.py
!docker-compose.example.yml

# ========================================
# FINAL SECURITY CHECK
# ========================================

# Ensure no common secret patterns slip through
*secret*
*password*
*token*
*credential*
*private*

# But allow these safe files
!*secret*.example
!*secret*.template
!*secret*.md
!password_requirements.md
!token_documentation.md